13:02.916 --> 13:04.584
Daniel: I just wanted
to know your opinion

13:04.617 --> 13:06.887
about what you think
the biggest differences are

13:06.920 --> 13:09.022
in the movement in America
and the movement here.

13:09.056 --> 13:11.458
I see the issues and the way
you've dealt with them

13:11.491 --> 13:12.893
is totally different.

13:12.926 --> 13:14.394
You know,
when you're gay or lesbian,

13:14.427 --> 13:16.529
you don't really form
part of the mainstream.

13:16.563 --> 13:19.566
You come out, and that's how you
have a gay subculture

13:19.599 --> 13:22.402
because you are really not
wanted in the family.

13:22.435 --> 13:25.105
But here, the gay
or lesbian children

13:25.138 --> 13:26.840
are left behind children

13:26.874 --> 13:29.209
because children
are a social treasure.

13:29.242 --> 13:33.446
So we may have to contend with
the more conservative movement.

13:33.480 --> 13:36.583
Even today,
there's no identity called gay.

13:36.616 --> 13:38.618
They say, "Are you this way?"

13:38.651 --> 13:42.555
It's widely stated that
you are the first person

13:42.589 --> 13:45.258
to say that...I'm gay.
-1982.

13:45.292 --> 13:46.860
-Yeah.
-Yeah.

13:46.894 --> 13:48.195
And, um, maybe you shou--

13:48.228 --> 13:50.363
could just give us
some context for that.

13:50.397 --> 13:54.301
I was a journalist
for approximately 28 years,

13:54.334 --> 13:56.636
and since then,
I've been in activism.

13:56.669 --> 13:59.139
It's been a bitter fight,

13:59.172 --> 14:02.876
both with the government
and within the community.

14:02.910 --> 14:05.913
Because within the community,
they're very divided.

14:05.946 --> 14:08.281
The women's issues
are totally different

14:08.315 --> 14:11.551
whereas the violence against
the men is in public spaces.

14:11.584 --> 14:13.553
In a way, men are cruising.

14:13.586 --> 14:18.258
For women, the violence is in --
in the domestic scene, you know?

14:18.291 --> 14:19.626
It's in closed spaces.

14:19.659 --> 14:22.395
That's where their oppression
takes place.

14:22.429 --> 14:25.432
There is a streak of misogyny
that has come in

14:25.465 --> 14:29.036
from the Western movements,
you know, to gay men here.

14:29.069 --> 14:32.039
But they don't like women
in gay bars, you know?

14:32.072 --> 14:34.507
You go out in the evenings
in many of Indian cities,

14:34.541 --> 14:37.310
there are no women
on the streets.

14:37.344 --> 14:40.380
They are just men.
Where are the women?

14:40.413 --> 14:43.250
Page: There are some
organizations

14:43.283 --> 14:45.085
fighting for community

14:45.118 --> 14:48.221
and visibility for lesbian
and bisexual women.

14:48.255 --> 14:49.389
