show you about this chamber.

27:04.891 --> 27:06.225
This is known
as "No karma" chambers.

27:06.258 --> 27:08.394
Nine different therapies
are working together,

27:08.427 --> 27:09.996
so when you're inside that,

27:10.029 --> 27:11.931
